---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact Us" description="Get in touch with the Rantique team.">
  <main class="prose prose-lg mx-auto py-12">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    <p>
      Have a question, suggestion, or collaboration in mind? We'd love to hear from you.
    </p>

    <h2>📬 Email</h2>
    <p>
      Reach us at: <a href="mailto:hello@rantique.com">hello@rantique.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>🌍 Social</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/rantique" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://instagram.com/rantique" target="_blank">Instagram</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://facebook.com/rantique" target="_blank">Facebook</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>📖 Submissions</h2>
    <p>
      Want to submit an article or short story? We're always looking for fresh voices. Please include a short bio, a brief pitch, and any links to your previous work.
    </p>

    <p class="italic text-gray-500">We read every message. Expect a response within 2–3 business days.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
